article.headline: Pruitt's 19 lead Lipscomb over Tennessee State 78-71

images.name: Tennessee State Tigers vs. Lipscomb Bisons: Full Highlights
images.caption: Tennessee State Tigers vs. Lipscomb Bisons: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Pruitt's 19 lead Lipscomb over Tennessee State 78-71
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Will Pruitt hit six straight free throws in the final 25 seconds and finished with 19 points in Lipscomb's 78-71 victory over Tennessee State on Sunday night. Pruitt added eight rebounds for the Bisons (7-5). Joe Anderson scored 15 points and added five assists. A.J McGinnis shot 2 for 9 (2 for 8 from 3-point range) and 7 of 8 from the free throw line to finish with 13 points. Christian Brown led the way for the Tigers (6-4) with 17 points. Jaylen Jones added 12 points and two steals for Tennessee State. In addition, EJ Bellinger had 12 points, two steals and two blocks. NEXT UP Lipscomb plays Saturday against Arkansas, and Tennessee State visits Liberty on Wednesday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
